<tt>'''util-linux'''</tt>是一个[[Linux|Linux]][[操作系统|操作系统]]的标准软件包。当开发停滞时，一群人创建了[[复刻_(软件工程)|复刻]]<tt>'''util-linux-ng'''</tt>（<tt>'''ng'''</tt>意为“下一代”）<ref>{{cite web
| title=<nowiki>[ANNOUNCE] util-linux-ng fork</nowiki>
| url=https://lkml.org/lkml/2006/12/18/19
| date=2006-12-18
| author=Karel Zak
| accessdate=2014-04-12
| archive-date=2014-04-13
| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413145412/https://lkml.org/lkml/2006/12/18/19
}}</ref>，但{{As of|2011|01|lc=on}}已更名回util-linux，目前是包的正式版本<ref>{{cite web
| title=<nowiki>[ANNOUNCE] util-linux without -ng</nowiki>
| url=https://lkml.org/lkml/2010/12/1/464
| date=2010-12-01
| author=Karel Zak
| accessdate=2014-04-12
| archive-date=2012-03-20
| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320012027/https://lkml.org/lkml/2010/12/1/464
}}</ref>。

